reviewText: Excellent DVD for the budding sheath maker.  Great on explanation and clarity, presented in a no-nonsense manner.  Highly recommended.
I have been doing leather work for the last 3-4 years and have always admired Chuck's work. This DVD was well worth the money alot of good tips

Another great DVD from Chuck Burrows. He takes the time to show step by step how to make a custom knife sheath. Takes a lot of guess work out of their construction with all kinds of tips and tricks along the way. I only wish he would do one on Indian bead work.
